==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Tape recorder
<hw>Tape recorder</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>an electronic
device for recording and playing back sounds on magnetic tape; it often
has an integrated microphone, amplifier, and speaker, and in such cases
requires no additional equipment other than the magnetic tape for
recording or playback.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tape recording</ent>⟦br⟧
